sentences.sentence: Attacks free oxygen radicals, and oxygenates the blood.

sentences.sentence: However, regarding selectivity towards oxygenates the relationship becomes the opposite.

sentences.sentence: The state of the art on fuel oxygenates, and in particular of MTBE in groundwater, is presented.
